data.value:
I really hope you will enjoy this software made with many source code (mine and from github)

This is for educational purposes only. This project will be open source on github. It aims to show you how works a kind of desktop environnement in VB.NET. You can also use src written in C#. Some of parts of this project won't be uploaded (like the others src (will put a link redirecting to this src) and my stubs) for not exactly copying this. I use many libraries like bunifu, telerik winform ui... if you don't have a version of bunifu (cracked or paid) , you won't be able to open this project.
